I like that idea But lets build several 25,000 ton Orion’s and send number one and two to the moon and soft land them there. The pioneer ships could be stripped and become the core of a Lunar industrial complex.  I am sure that a suitable site could be found that features:<br>
<br>
1) Some water ice<br>
2) A huge chunk of a metallic meteorite (Fe + Ni)<br>
3) A suitable soil composition that includes high concentrations of Al and Mg and other valuable minerals.<br>
<br>
