<br>
I guess at first just the hulls, pusher plates, shock absorbers and structural components would be produced and assembled into new ships with the lightweight high technology stuff being ferried to the Lunar base by Orion3.  <br>
<br>
Orion 3 could be an Earth to Moon ferry that transports whatever can’t yet be produced on the moon from LEO to the base in a continuous cycle. <br>
<br>
Orion 4 gets the fun job of doing a detailed search of the asteroid belt along with many scientific missions. Orion 4 could release a hundreds robotic prospectors into the belt. Small asteroids crammed with mineral wealth would be identified and marked for exploitation. <br>
<br>
Damn the prospects are just endless.<br>
